{"tid":1631392,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[心痛] 好多年輕前線手足被捕","createTime":"2019-10-06T15:24:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T15:28:39.000Z","uid":315195,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"46430b16b7711045543c31213167dd8a60903ece","tid":1631392,"uid":315195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:24:48.000Z","msg":"我係一個和理非，周不時發夢做下物資鏈。<br />\n<br />\n近期每一次發夢，黑警會放大家行，但去到一半就狗沖出黎捉人...<br />\n<br />\n好多時前線手足為左和理非，而要殿後，搞到要送頭。（今日電視上面好多都好細個）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FwuYC3c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFwuYC3c.jpg&h=a80d80ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n為左保護年輕既前線，有一個建議。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">日頭：全和理非遊行。勇武都要變和理非，不戀戰，不被捕，be water, 減輕前線壓力。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">入夜：先轉返勇武前線，大搞快閃十八區。一來可以減低前線被捕，又可以比人睇下我地和平遊行，減低轉風向問題。<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">大家都想呢場仗贏，唔好白流血，要令犧牲左嘅手足得有價值，一定要同黑警轉玩法。</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n另外，希望手足唔好撩軍營。由開始到依家都四個月，有幾大獲都好，暫時都未見老解。要出都要佢地自己出，唔係因為xxx而老解出動，場運動就輸撚硬。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">最後，獅鳥一定要出師有名。咪撚打錯人<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n香港人， 反抗！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U3g4yCT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU3g4yCT.jpg&h=b4f3417c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"87851102c8cb0257a006f01e2d63d4d82cec8440","tid":1631392,"uid":315195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:26:00.000Z","msg":"自推10連"},{"pid":"1a9524da39c208fe19cad51cd4c74c8818a55026","tid":1631392,"uid":315195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:26:21.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"7714c3c4fa5684c6d9d8ab9ceb22b4aa9f650b62","tid":1631392,"uid":315195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:26:49.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"f8eda0571655f535dcc8b09ef363159468357cdb","tid":1631392,"uid":315195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:27:01.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"51730afb689d119bd5e4d55f94020f829590c592","tid":1631392,"uid":315195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:27:11.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"c6d6ea6ba0dd9fd375944242d8d2ea0d5bff96bc","tid":1631392,"uid":315195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:27:29.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"3421aa1512c87375aad0977095e4570f130ef766","tid":1631392,"uid":315195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:27:40.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"339f1e0e2d375d852bb282b6c212e962e16d11ec","tid":1631392,"uid":315195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:27:57.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"ab8f067984838c809409e46c2d63199c01941dfa","tid":1631392,"uid":315195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:28:11.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"570afd3a6f68683a8d2b52c2ad1e675178efffb7","tid":1631392,"uid":315195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:28:25.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"597bc94326de3cb95c71c1f6a1ba4f49f4c16010","tid":1631392,"uid":315195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:28:39.000Z","msg":"10"}]}